T02TD2380E:12b-1: tsa tur yo ga bh'a ba na n'a ma /
T02TD2380E:12b-3: rnal 'byor bzhi'i nyams len gyi thabs zhes bya ba /
T02TD2380E:12b-4: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2380E:12b-5: sems dang sems nyid rgyu med de //
T02TD2380E:12b-6: bsgrub bya sgrub byed thig la'i ngo //
T02TD2380E:12b-8: dpal ldan dpa' bo yi ge med //
T02TD2380E:12b-9: lte bar gsang ba'i ge sar la //
T02TD2380E:12b-10: a'a li k'a li la brten nas //
T02TD2380E:12b-11: rnal 'byor bzhi yi nyams len bshad //
T02TD2380E:12b-12: lte ba yi shes 'khor lo ru //
T02TD2380E:12b-13: rtsa ni brgyad kyi thig btab nas //
T02TD2380E:12b-14: a'a phreng k'a phreng mnyam bsams nas //
T02TD2380E:12b-15: mkha' 'gro brgyad kyi me lce sbar //
T02TD2380E:12b-16: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni //
T02TD2380E:12b-17: nam mkha'i dbyibs kyi 'od las ni //
T02TD2380E:12b-19: dpa' bo rnams kyi lam nas rgyu //
T02TD2380E:12b-22: sangs rgyas rnams kyi sa lam thob //
T02TD2380E:12b-23: a'a li k'a li'i rnal 'byor ro //
T02TD2380E:12b-24: aa ho bzlas pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
T02TD2380E:12b-25: dngos dang dngos med bral 'gyur bas //
T02TD2380E:13a-4: rdo rje sems dpa' dang mnyam mo //
T02TD2380E:13a-5: de ni rig ba'i rnal 'byor ro //
T02TD2380E:13a-6: sems nyid gnas su padma ni //
T02TD2380E:13a-7: mnyam pa nyid ni dmar por bsam //
T02TD2380E:13a-8: pad 'dab bzhi la thig le ni //
T02TD2380E:13a-9: dbus su rgyu med thig le yin //
T02TD2380E:13a-10: de dag rnams kyi kha dog ni //
T02TD2380E:13a-11: shar du dmar dang byang du ser //
T02TD2380E:13a-12: nub tu dkar dang lho ru gnag / sna tshogs 'od gsal dbus su 'phro //
T02TD2380E:13a-13: sngar bshad sngags dang bcas pa ni //
T02TD2380E:13a-14: sgom na rnal 'byor dbang phyug de //
T02TD2380E:13a-15: skad cig gcig la rdzogs sangs rgyas //
T02TD2380E:13a-16: de ni mnyam nyid rnal 'byor ro //
T02TD2380E:13a-17: mi bskyod chu dang rnam snang dang //
T02TD2380E:13a-18: phyi nang bdud rtsi lnga yis ni //
T02TD2380E:13a-19: sngags pa'i thabs kyi rnal 'byor gyi //
T02TD2380E:13a-20: tan ti bdag gis grub pa thob //
T02TD2380E:13a-21: rnal 'byor bzhi'i nyams len ces bya ba slob dpon tan ti pas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
